CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to output the value of the selected radio item.

CustomProperties.Name: Label
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to set if a label is to be shown.

CustomProperties.Name: DisplayMode
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to set the display mode of the radio buttons.

CustomProperties.Name: onSelect
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to trigger an action when a radio button is selected.

Rules.InvariantScript:
//Use the RenameColumns to insert your own column names from a Data source.
Table({radioItem:"New York"},{radioItem:"Dallas"},{radioItem:"Tampa"},{radioItem:"Detroit"})
If(IsBlank('Radio Button'.DefaultSelected), {}, LookUp('Radio Button'.RadioButtonItems, radioItem = 'Radio Button'.DefaultSelected))
If(ThisItem.IsSelected = true, If('Radio Button'.PrimaryOrange = true, ColorValue("#D04A02"), ColorValue("#415385")), ColorValue("#2D2D2D"))
